WWW-Scraper-Flickr
==================

This modules enables you to scrape metadata of Flickr pictures
and even download images.

Please use it for personal and good endeavours only. (Everything
else would not be allowed by Flickr's TOS anyway.)
Always remember to to make the Internets a better place for all of us.


USAGE

You'll probably use this module via the included scripts. Have a look
into the script dir for source and they'll be installed by default.

INSTALLATION

Nothing special. To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

